Fixed variable declaration:
    - Now you can't create variable names the same as keywords
        - No panic: const number = 2; -> const _number = 2;
Optimized variable declaration: [ast]
    - Now the optimizer sets the type of the variable to the literal's type if the variable's type is "auto"
Added function "ast::optimizer::ExpressionToType(ast::Expr*)"
Added literal folding for Number-Number (<, <=, >, >=, !=, -)